<h1>About Disappearing City</h1>
<div style="word-wrap: break-word; width: 550px" <<p>An app for when you forget to remember cities as you once knew them. Using the Open Weather API,
Disappearing City displays an rainy image of a city if the API returns the weather status as 'rain' or 'mist'. If the API returns
the weather status as anything else (i.e, sunny, cloudy), Disappearing City returns a sunny image of a city.</p></div>
